Built on OpenZeppelinâ€™s audited ERC-20 stack:

- ðŸ” **Ownable** â€” restricts mint / burn / pause to the platform owner  
- ðŸ›‘ **ERC20Pausable** â€” emergency freeze of transfers  
- ðŸ”¨ **Mint** â€” controlled token creation  
- ðŸ”¥ **Burn** â€” voluntary supply reduction (users or owner)  
- â¸ **Pause / Unpause** â€” circuit breaker for exploits

---

## âš™ï¸ Functional Features


| Function      | Description                  | Access       |
|---------------|------------------------------|--------------|
| `mint()`      | Mint new tokens              | Only Owner   |
| `burn()`      | Burn user-held tokens        | Any Holder   |
| `pause()`     | Pause all token transfers    | Only Owner   |
| `unpause()`   | Resume paused transfers      | Only Owner   |

| Item             | Value                    |
|------------------|--------------------------|
| **Total Supply** | 1 000 000 000 HNT       |
| **Initial Mint** | 100 000 000 HNT (10 %) |
| **Decimals**     | 18                       |

